name: Onyx 2
Lore: 'Part of limited production run of TIE defenders. Testing of the prototype defender indicated the need for a more powerful hyperdrive, which was added for this production model.',
Text: 'Deploys for free to any mobile system. May deploy with a pilot as a ''react''. May add 1 pilot. Any starship cannon may deploy aboard. Immune to attriton < 4 when Yorr piloting.',
